{"type": "article", "id": 18364, "title": "鹿角灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-02T07:20:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 154, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060615314668UJi7lLEhopsc94.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这盏用硬纸板做的壁灯有一个像动物头一样的外形，它真正的设计在灯光的形状，开灯后两束像鹿角一样的光线从两只耳朵边上发射出去，而中心的光源也会让“鹿头”显得更加立体，简单而巧妙。设计师从儿童的立体书里获得灵感，它非常适合即将到来的圣诞节。售价 90 美元，<a href=\"http://popuplighting.com/collections/all-items/products/single-deer-head-an-elegant-cardboard-wall-led-light-fixture\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153143mvLFdhbs7r5cQp0k.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.00833333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153144RZbNFJxI2h34QCaW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061531454RcFf8Z2xDvKw1lb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153145pJSzN7ZTMeYxL9qh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153146b1awuOKptIj6i9Mh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}